subject: Request for Permission to Move In Between 7 PM and 11 PM.
message:
Hi All,

I hope this email finds you well. My name is Srishti Rawat, and I am a student at BCU. I would like to inform you that my flight from Delhi has been delayed by approximately 3 hours, which will result in my late arrival in Birmingham.

Given that this is my first time in the country, and considering the challenges of navigating a new city, particularly as a female student, I kindly request your permission to move in between 7 PM and 11 PM. I understand that this may not be the ideal time, but due to the circumstances, I would greatly appreciate your understanding and support.

Thank you for considering my request, and I look forward to your response.
Best regards,
Srishti Rawat
